Merge branch 'topic/1337' into 'master'

Make `inst_params` parameters instance-aware.

Closes #1339 and #1337

See merge request eng/libadalang/libadalang!1599

Make ``inst_params`` parameters instance-aware.

Also update the zip_with_params implementation to behave similarly.
Return a more precise type for the `designated_generic_decl` property.

Merge branch 'topic/libadalang-internal-testsuite/13' into 'master'

gnat_compare: fix short flag for --skip-gprclean option

See merge request eng/libadalang/libadalang!1606

gnat_compare: fix short flag for --skip-gprclean option

Short flag used for `--skip-gprclean` was set to `-C` which is already
taken as the short for `--charset`. Changing it to `-sc` instead.

Merge branch 'topic/is_spark_mode_again' into 'master'

Refactor is_spark_impl to handle explicit `SPARK_Mode => Off` correctly

Closes #1343

See merge request eng/libadalang/libadalang!1600

Refactor is_spark_impl to handle explicit `SPARK_Mode => Off` correctly

`is_spark_impl` has been refactored into `spark_mode_aspect`, which
rather than returning just a boolean for "On/Off", returns an aspect,
which contains the information "On/Off/no information".

This in turns allow to implement the logic "either take the value from
the aspect, and if there is none, take the value from the .adc".
